The carnival of ultimate frisbee lunacy in Amsterdam originated in 2005 and is completely run by a community of volunteers. This year we expect around 1400 players from all over Europe to join. The three days are to be packed with hardcore ultimate and exiting amusement in relaxed Amsterdam-style atmosphere.
